sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User / Job Seeker
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant DB as Database
    participant NS as Notification System

    User->>FE: Open portal
    FE->>BE: Request job listings
    BE->>DB: Fetch jobs, companies, filters
    DB-->>BE: Job data
    BE-->>FE: Return job listings
    FE-->>User: Show searchable job list

    User->>FE: Search / filter / sort jobs
    FE->>BE: Send search criteria
    BE->>DB: Query matching jobs
    DB-->>BE: Matching results
        actor User as Job Seeker
        participant FE as Frontend
        participant BE as Backend
        participant DB as Database
        participant NS as Notification System

        User->>FE: Open portal
        FE->>BE: Request available jobs
        BE->>DB: Fetch jobs and company data
        DB-->>BE: Job list
        BE-->>FE: Return job list
        FE-->>User: Display jobs

        User->>FE: Search, filter, or sort jobs
        FE->>BE: Send search criteria
        BE->>DB: Query matching jobs
        DB-->>BE: Matching results
        BE-->>FE: Return filtered jobs
        FE-->>User: Show results

        User->>FE: View job details and apply
        FE->>BE: Submit application and resume
        BE->>DB: Save application
        DB-->>BE: Application stored
        BE->>NS: Send confirmation email
        NS-->>User: Application confirmation
        BE-->>FE: Application submitted
        FE-->>User: Show success message

        User->>FE: Save job to wishlist
        FE->>BE: Store saved job
        BE->>DB: Save wishlist item
        DB-->>BE: Saved successfully
        BE-->>FE: Wishlist updated
        FE-->>User: Confirm saved job

        Note over BE,NS: Employer can update status or schedule interviews
        BE->>NS: Send status update or interview email
        NS-->>User: Notification email